│ 1726 ///  * VPScalarIVStepsRecipe: Generates scalar values per-lane based on a         │
│ 1727 ///    canonical or derived induction.                                            │
│ 1728 ///  * VPWidenPointerInductionRecipe: Generate vector and scalar values for a     │
